    "body": "## Summary                                                                                                                                                                                  \n                                                                \n  Extracts KV-cache update from FlexAttention, one of the last backends still doing it inline. Part of #32335.                                                                                \n                                                                                   \n  ## What this does                                                                                                                                                                           \n                                                                                   \n  FlexAttention was still calling `reshape_and_cache_flash` inside `forward()`. This PR pulls it out into `do_kv_cache_update()` and sets the flag to `False`, same as FlashAttn, FlashInfer,\n  Triton, and the ROCm backends already do.\n\n  ## Test plan\n\n  - `tests/v1/attention/test_attention_backends.py` already handles the split path based on the flag\n  - `tests/kernels/test_flex_attention.py` compares FlexAttention output against the default backend\n",
    "created_at": "2026-03-06T16:29:31Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-03-09T03:41:10Z",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-09T03:40:12Z",
